des:
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the air purifier. There's no need to go to the switch to adjust your unit, just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.

After connecting Alexa to your enviroboss Smart in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "enviroboss" in android or ios app market;
(2) Register one account in our "enviroboss" app;
(3) You need to have some enviroboss smart devices in hand;
(4) Configure these devices in our "enviroboss" app and change the appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "enviroboss" skill;
(5) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6) Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7) Search "enviroboss" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8) Click Enable skill of "enviroboss", and you'll be navigated to enviroboss login page;
(9) Follow the instructions on the page to complete the linking;

Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your air purifier like these:
"Alexa, turn on DEVICENAME."
"Alexa, turn off DEVICENAME."
"Alexa, turn on child lock on the DEVICENAME."
"Alexa, turn off child lock on the DEVICENAME."
"Alexa, set DEVICENAME fan speed to one."
"Alexa, set DEVICENAME fan speed to two."
"Alexa, set DEVICENAME fan speed to three."
"Alexa, set DEVICENAME fan speed to auto."
